name: Agents vs Aliens
description:
https://levidsmith.com/games/agents-vs-aliens/

Agents vs Aliens is a MOBA (multiplayer online battle arena) style arena game, where you control a team of agents to conquer the battlefield.

Controls:

Right click to move around on the battlefield.

Right click the enemy champion or enemy core to attack.

Move mouse wheel to zoom in and out.
